modName: Female Preset for Hallgarth's Snow Elf Race - The True Falmer
summary: A preset for this amazing race mod.
descriptionHtml:
Manually download and extract to Data/SKSE/Plugins/Chargen/Presets.

I cannot make a male preset because I heavily edited them on my end with the CK and made them look like this mod: [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/56685/?]Lester[/url]

Mods used are here on this image: [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/images/578448/?]http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/images/578448/?[/url]

[u]NOTES[/u]
[list]
[*][size=2]Preset will say that it requires Northborn Scars but that can be safely ignored it will not affect how your character looks in-game.[/size]
[size=2]
[/size][*][size=2]Picture 3 (near shrine to Talos) is what your character will look like with Fair Skin Complexion if you follow my tutorial above. The first two are with a different texture linked at the bottom of said tutorial.[/size]
[/list]
author: RavenSterling
